   Shah, Majid Hussain, Univ Alabama, Dept Geol Sci, Tuscaloosa, AL 35487 USA.
   Kouki, Marouan, Northern Border Univ, Fac Comp \& Informat Technol, Dept Informat Syst, Rafha, Saudi Arabia.
