Affiliation = {Baek, JY (Corresponding Author), Univ Ulsan, Asan Med Ctr, Dept Internal Med, Div Geriatr,Coll Med, 88 Olymp Ro 43 Gil, Seoul, South Korea.
   Ji, Sunghwan; Lee, Yura, Univ Ulsan, Coll Med, Asan Med Ctr, Dept Informat Med, Seoul, South Korea.
   Ji, Sunghwan, Sungkyunkwan Univ, Dept Digital Hlth, SAIHST, Seoul, South Korea.
