   Galitsyna, Aleksandra A.; Khrameeva, Ekaterina E.; Gelfand, Mikhail S., Skolkovo Inst Sci \& Technol, Moscow, Russia.
   Sapunov, Grigory, V, Intento Inc, Berkeley, CA USA.
   Gelfand, Mikhail S., RAS, AA Kharkevich Inst Informat Transmiss Problems, Moscow, Russia.},
DOI = {10.7717/pearj-cs.307},
