   network; Genetic algorithm; Alloy design},
Keywords-Plus = {ARTIFICIAL NEURAL-NETWORKS; 700 DEGREES-C; MATERIALS DISCOVERY; TENSILE
   PROPERTIES; GENETIC ALGORITHM; CREEP DEFORMATION; ADAPTIVE DESIGN;
